# NOTICE: AI Utilization and Intellectual Property Policy

This project values open-source collaboration, but firmly stands against the predatory extraction of intellectual labor via automation. Please read the following terms, warnings, and retroactive authorization policies carefully.

---

## English Version

### CRITICAL WARNING & PROHIBITION
Any form of utilizing this project's achievements—including but not limited to its source code, architectural logic, user interface designs, and **page screenshots**—to feed into Artificial Intelligence (AI), Large Language Models (LLMs), or any automated tools for reading, analysis, or the generation of similar, functional, or visual look-alikes is **STRICTLY PROHIBITED** by the project authors.

We issue this solemn warning against any "AI-assisted plagiarism" or "code/design laundering." While we embrace the open-source spirit, we do not tolerate the parasitic exploitation of our hard work under the guise of AI re-generation.

### HOW TO OBTAIN AUTHORIZATION (COMMERCIAL USE INCLUDED)
We are not against collaboration. If you wish to use, adapt, or build upon our work, you can do so legitimately by **contacting us directly to obtain explicit authorization**. 
* **In most cases, we will gladly grant permission—even for commercial projects**—provided that an open dialogue is established and terms are mutually agreed upon. 

### RETROACTIVE AUTHORIZATION & AMNESTY CLAUSE
If you have **already utilized** any achievements of this project prior to reading this notice (including but not limited to feeding source code, architectural logic, or page screenshots into AI for reading, analysis, or replication), you are encouraged to contact us immediately to apply for **retroactive authorization**.

* **Evidence Preservation:** Please be advised that we have already monitored the market and **fully preserved relevant evidence** regarding existing products or projects suspected of plagiarizing our achievements.
* **Amnesty Policy:** For individuals or entities who proactively reach out to us and successfully complete the retroactive authorization process, **we will formally waive our right to pursue any legal liability.**

### ENFORCEMENT & LITIGATION
Any unauthorized plagiarism, replication, or AI-assisted reproduction discovered without our explicit written consent (and without a retroactive authorization agreement) will be treated as a willful violation of our rights. **We will take immediate and rigorous legal actions, including but not limited to lawsuits, injunctions, and public copyright claims, to protect our intellectual property.**

Please respect the true open-source spirit. Respecting the creator is the foundation of the community.

### 厳重警告および禁止事項
本プロジェクトの成果物（ソースコード、設計ロジック、UIデザイン、および**ページのスクリーンショット**を含みますが、これらに限定されません）を、人工知能（AI）、大規模言語モデル（LLM）、またはその他の自動化ツールに読み込ませ、分析・学習させ、類似する機能や視覚的効果を持つ成果物を生成させる行為は、いかなる形式であれ、開発者の意思として**固く禁止**します。

AIを隠れ蓑にした「プラグマティズム（盗用）」や「コードロンダリング（成果物の洗浄）」に対し、ここに厳重に警告します。私たちはオープンソースの精神を深く尊重していますが、AI生成という名目のもとで私たちの労働成果を不當に搾取する行為は一切容認しません。

### 利用許諾の取得について（商用利用を含む）
私たちは技術の発展や協力を拒絶しているわけではありません。本プロジェクトの成果を利用、または参考にしたい場合は、**事前に私たちに連絡し、明示的な許諾を得てください**。
* **適切なコミュニケーションが行われれば、商用プロジェクトであっても、多くの場合において利用を快く承認します。** 筋を通したアプローチを歓迎します。

